description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Parvati purrs with a rating of 98, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 196, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and 3 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [196 Votes, Hall of Fame]
